<html>
<body>
This skill improves a warrior's ability to block attacks with a shield. <br>
Without the skill a shield will have some defensive value, but being<br>
adept at the use of a shield increases this drastically.<br>
<br>
This is a passive skill, in that there is no need to type in any command<br>
for an attempt at shield blocking.<br>
